<br>
put like 100 people, to take behemoth on.  then get like another 60, put 2 groups in each room where the clocks pop in.  2 groups can take out clocks forever, heck, can even get some xp from them if your people are like 61 or 62.<br>
<br>
my point was the way those zones are designed (barring a zone crash from overload) there is no maximum limit to people participating.  if you fail you can add 50 more and go again, and 50 more and 50 more...<br>
